Define a function called greet that takes name and does the following.
  Say hello, name.
End function.

Define a function called add that takes a and b and does the following.
  Give back a plus b.
End function.

Define a function called multiply that takes a and b and does the following.
  Give back a times b.
End function.

Define a function called factorial that takes n and does the following.
  If n is less than 2 then do the following.
    Give back 1.
  End if.
  Let smaller be n minus 1.
  Let sub be the result of calling factorial with smaller.
  Give back n times sub.
End function.

Define a function called power that takes base and exp and does the following.
  Let result be 1.
  While exp is greater than 0 do the following.
    Let result be result times base.
    Let exp be exp minus 1.
  End while.
  Give back result.
End function.

