Let sum be the result of calling add with 3, 5.
Say 3 plus 5 equals, sum.

Let product be the result of calling multiply with 6, 7.
Say 6 times 7 equals, product.

Let fact5 be the result of calling factorial with 5.
Say factorial of 5 is, fact5.

Let twoPow10 be the result of calling power with 2, 10.
Say 2 to the power of 10 is, twoPow10.
